@startuml
title UC: Watch Live Traffic Camera

actor "User" as U
boundary "Map UI" as MAP
control "CameraBrowseController" as CBC
entity "Camera" as C
participant "LiveStreamService" as LIVE

U -> MAP: Click camera pin on map
MAP -> CBC: selectCamera(cameraId)

CBC -> C: findById(cameraId)
C --> CBC: cameraDetails(url, location)

CBC -> LIVE: requestLiveStream(cameraDetails.url)
LIVE --> CBC: streamToken + streamUrl

CBC --> MAP: showCameraPanel(cameraDetails)\n+ attach streamUrl
MAP --> U: Live video starts playing

@enduml